📘 Legal Calculus — Module 90

The Filing Trap

⚖️ Core Message

Filing alone isn’t enough. If format, caption, and title aren’t precise, the court may treat your filing as if it never existed.

📖 Lesson Content

1. See full pack for detailed steps.
2. Title and caption correctly.
3. Numbered facts + Certificate of Service.
4. Preserve the record with short notices.

📝 Assignment

Draft the short notice/template referenced in this module (see consolidated PDF for examples).

